  Main Activity    [in APK]         MainActivity.onCreate() apk/ui/MainActivity.kt
  Stub APK         stub-release.apk StubApplication.java   stub/StubApplication.java
  Boot patching    [script]         boot_patch.sh          scripts/boot_patch.sh
  Module install   [script]         module_installer.sh   scripts/module_installer.sh


