      |   +-- uninstaller.sh         (script)
      |   +-- module_installer.sh    (script)
      |   +-- flash_script.sh        (script)
      |   +-- bootctl                (binary)
      |   +-- chromeos/
      |   |   +-- futility           (binary)
      |   |   +-- kernel_data_key.vbprivk
      |   |   +-- kernel.keyblock
      |   +-- META-INF/com/google/android/
      |   |   +-- update-binary      (script)
      |   |   +-- updater-script     (script)
      |   +-- stub.apk               (embedded stub APK)
      |
      +-- res/                       (UI resources)
      +-- kotlin/                    (Kotlin metadata)
      +-- res/xml/backup_rules.xml   (backup rules)

  Native Binary Details:
    Binary          Type         Linked Libraries          Size (approx)
    -------         ----         ----------------          -------------
    magisk          executable   libbase, libsystemprops,  ~1.5-2MB
                                 liblsplt, libmagisk-rs
    magiskinit      static exe   libbase, libpolicy,       ~500-700KB
                                 libxz, libinit-rs, crt0
    magiskboot      static exe   libbase, liblz4,          ~400-600KB
                                 libboot-rs, crt0
    magiskpolicy    executable   libbase, libpolicy,       ~300-400KB
                                 libpolicy-rs
    libinit-ld.so   shared lib   (none, minimal)           ~10-15KB


================================================================================
11. SCRIPTS REFERENCE
================================================================================

  boot_patch.sh     - Main boot image patching script
    Usage: boot_patch.sh <boot_image>
    Env: KEEPVERITY, KEEPFORCEENCRYPT, PATCHVBMETAFLAG, RECOVERYMODE, LEGACYSAR
    Flow:
      1. Extract boot image with magiskboot
      2. CPIO: Add magiskinit, overlay files
      3. DTB: Patch fstab (remove verify/encrypt)
      4. Repack with magiskboot
      5. Sign if needed

  module_installer.sh - Magisk module installer script
    Usage: (called from recovery or Magisk Manager)
    Flow:
      1. Extract module ZIP to tmp dir
      2. Read module.prop for metadata
      3. Create /data/adb/modules/<id>/
      4. Copy files preserving directory structure
      5. Remove update.json if present
      6. Clean up temp files

  flash_script.sh   - Recovery flashable zip script
  update_binary.sh  - Recovery update-binary script
    Used in META-INF/com/google/android/ for recovery flashing

  addon.d.sh        - OTA survival script
    Preserves Magisk across OTA updates

  uninstaller.sh    - Uninstall script
    Removes all Magisk components

  app_functions.sh  - App helper functions
    Used by the APK to interface with scripts

  util_functions.sh - Shared utility functions
    Functions used by all other scripts:
      - get_flashable_image()
      - find_boot_image()
      - flash_image()
      - etc.

  release.sh        - Release script (for maintainers)
  live_setup.sh     - AVD emulator setup
  host_patch.sh     - AVD host patching
  test_common.sh    - Common test utilities
  cuttlefish.sh     - Cuttlefish emulator support


